,"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"你、你也不用嚇這麼大一跳吧……\n剛剛謝謝你，幫忙製作裝飾喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event265-05-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":228}],"windowDisplayName":"夏洛特","body":"……我真的是無法理解耶。\n為什麼你們可以這麼地樂觀？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":228,"motionName":"sigh01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":228,"voiceId":"event265-05-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":228}],"windowDisplayName":"夏洛特","body":"我可是你們的敵人喔？\n但是你們卻這麼喜歡來找我，這樣不是很怪嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":228,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":228,"voiceId":"event265-05-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"會嗎……但我們幾個之中，沒有人把三園同學你\n當成是我們的敵人啊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event265-05-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"不只是這樣……還會